{"tid":2199804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（正視聽）十一國殤唔係最後一戰","createTime":"2020-09-12T13:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T02:53:55.000Z","uid":146917,"like":36,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb5ce4e7e746182bc5d76509bfa9e6519528ced","tid":2199804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"國殤日唔會係最後一戰<br />\n但會係盛大既一戰<br />\n果日完左 抗爭仍然會繼續落去<br />\n直至5大訴求完全達到<br />\n我地係打持久戰<br />\n所以我懇請每一位真香港人 <br />\n果日齊齊整整出去<br />\n就齊齊整整番屋企<br />\n除左班狗<br />\n祝各位武運昌隆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n願榮光歸香光"},{"pid":"dabb8597c9825301373fd3f7380a51263f6d1812","tid":2199804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a34e76d4f0ca0890dc81ab3e9b5338a50a7edd8","tid":2199804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6606b3ea9ea9f66ede3ef6ab47c046dd34a661","tid":2199804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b4d5e8a5ab985b323bd39448a6c41798308252","tid":2199804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f330d14aa29097466bb2cefe72fe1e59bd42096","tid":2199804,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"五毛退散文：<br />\n<br />\n【爆po再開】遊行冇用，勇武冇用，黃經濟圈冇用，罷工冇用，黎明冇用，民意逆轉，開始攰，送頭，中計，係鬼，前線死嗮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778543</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6902dd75e1e381f909c7004d8b774f290042416a","tid":2199804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite